title: Sew - April 2015
description:
If you love to stitch, or want to learn, then Sew is the magazine for you! Jam-packed full of stylish projects for your wardrobe and your home, there's something for all interests and abilities including dressmaking, patchwork and quilting, embroidery and more. 

In addition, you'll find practical advice from leading industry experts, plus the latest stitching news, interviews, giveaways and more.

Genre: Magazine
